Sentencas: In this study, the unusual microstructure and electrical properties of SmBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+d (SBSCO) layered perovskite cathodes with dense and porous microstructures were analyzed by changing the applied current.
Titulo: Generation of nanoflowers and nanoneedles on Co-based layered perovskite of IT-SOFC cathode affecting electrical conductivities

Sentencas: Unique nanostructure shapes were observed when a high current was applied to a cathode with both dense and porous microstructures of the same chemical composition for electrical conductivity measurement.
Titulo: Generation of nanoflowers and nanoneedles on Co-based layered perovskite of IT-SOFC cathode affecting electrical conductivities

Sentencas: Nanoflower and nanoneedles, which are types of nanoseeds, were discovered.
Titulo: Generation of nanoflowers and nanoneedles on Co-based layered perovskite of IT-SOFC cathode affecting electrical conductivities

Sentencas: The nanoneedles were found on the entire surface of the SBSCO cathode, whereas nanoflowers were only present on part of the cathode surface.
Titulo: Generation of nanoflowers and nanoneedles on Co-based layered perovskite of IT-SOFC cathode affecting electrical conductivities

Sentencas: Results from an Energy Dispersive Spectrometer (EDS) analysis revealed that the nanoneedles generated on the SBSCO matrix had a chemical composition of SmBaCo2O5+d (SBCO).The electrical conductivity of the porous cathode with SBCO nanoneedles (nanoneedle cathode) was 238 S/cm at 700 degrees C under decreasing temperature in an air atmosphere (Air Down) during the experiment.
Titulo: Generation of nanoflowers and nanoneedles on Co-based layered perovskite of IT-SOFC cathode affecting electrical conductivities

Sentencas: In comparison, the electrical conductivity of the porous cathode without nanoneedles (normal cathode) was 136 S/cm at the same experiment condition (700 degrees C, Air Down).
Titulo: Generation of nanoflowers and nanoneedles on Co-based layered perovskite of IT-SOFC cathode affecting electrical conductivities

Sentencas: This indicates that the electrical conductivity of the nano-needle cathode was significantly higher than that of the normal cathode.(c) 2023
Titulo: Generation of nanoflowers and nanoneedles on Co-based layered perovskite of IT-SOFC cathode affecting electrical conductivities
